title: YGIG
text:
YGIG /Y·G·I·G/ (You Go, I Go) is a five-member Filipino girl group under SBTown. The members consist of Vien, Jewel, Hazelyn, Maeg, and Alexei. They made their official debut on November 25, 2022 with their first single Shaba Shaba. YGIG aims to represent the Filipino female groups in the international scene.


== Members ==
Current
Alexei
Hazelyn
Jewel
Maeg
Vien - leader

Darlene (2022-2023)
